{
    "publish_date": "2013-03-20T16:12:21.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT12M16S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "When I was little,", 
            "dur": "1.351", 
            "start": "15.357"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought my country was the best on the planet,", 
            "dur": "3.362", 
            "start": "16.708"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I grew up singing a song called &quot;Nothing To Envy.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.375", 
            "start": "20.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I was very proud.", 
            "dur": "2.635", 
            "start": "23.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In school, we spent a lot of time", 
            "dur": "1.788", 
            "start": "26.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "studying the history of Kim Il-Sung,", 
            "dur": "1.761", 
            "start": "27.868"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but we never learned much about the outside world,", 
            "dur": "3.942", 
            "start": "29.629"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "except that America, South Korea, Japan are the enemies.", 
            "dur": "4.95", 
            "start": "33.571"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Although I often wondered about the outside world,", 
            "dur": "3.214", 
            "start": "38.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought I would spend my entire life in North Korea,", 
            "dur": "4.148", 
            "start": "41.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "until everything suddenly changed.", 
            "dur": "3.704", 
            "start": "45.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I was seven years old, I saw my first public execution,", 
            "dur": "4.76", 
            "start": "49.587"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I thought my life in North Korea was normal.", 
            "dur": "3.258", 
            "start": "54.347"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My family was not poor,", 
            "dur": "2.112", 
            "start": "57.605"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and myself, I had never experienced hunger.", 
            "dur": "3.533", 
            "start": "59.717"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But one day, in 1995, my mom brought home a letter", 
            "dur": "4.503", 
            "start": "63.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from a coworker&#39;s sister.", 
            "dur": "2.063", 
            "start": "67.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It read, &quot;When you read this, all five family members", 
            "dur": "5.134", 
            "start": "69.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "will not exist in this world,", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "74.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we haven&#39;t eaten for the past two weeks.", 
            "dur": "4.151", 
            "start": "77.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We are lying on the floor together,", 
            "dur": "2.472", 
            "start": "81.841"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and our bodies are so weak we are ready to die.&quot;", 
            "dur": "8.711", 
            "start": "84.313"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was so shocked.", 
            "dur": "3.307", 
            "start": "93.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This was the first time I heard", 
            "dur": "2.146", 
            "start": "96.331"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that people in my country were suffering.", 
            "dur": "4.237", 
            "start": "98.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Soon after, when I was walking past a train station,", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "102.714"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I saw something terrible", 
            "dur": "1.385", 
            "start": "106.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I can&#39;t erase from my memory.", 
            "dur": "3.824", 
            "start": "107.409"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A lifeless woman was lying on the ground,", 
            "dur": "3.168", 
            "start": "111.233"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "while an emaciated child in her arms", 
            "dur": "3.189", 
            "start": "114.401"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just stared helplessly at his mother&#39;s face.", 
            "dur": "4.41", 
            "start": "117.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But nobody helped them, because they were so focused", 
            "dur": "4.24", 
            "start": "122"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on taking care of themselves and their families.", 
            "dur": "4.625", 
            "start": "126.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A huge famine hit North Korea in the mid-1990s.", 
            "dur": "4.117", 
            "start": "130.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ultimately, more than a million North Koreans", 
            "dur": "2.735", 
            "start": "134.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "died during the famine, and many only survived", 
            "dur": "3.317", 
            "start": "137.717"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by eating grass, bugs and tree bark.", 
            "dur": "5.649", 
            "start": "141.034"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Power outages also became more and more frequent,", 
            "dur": "3.284", 
            "start": "146.683"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so everything around me was completely dark at night", 
            "dur": "4.357", 
            "start": "149.967"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "except for the sea of lights in China,", 
            "dur": "2.552", 
            "start": "154.324"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just across the river from my home.", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "156.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I always wondered why they had lights but we didn&#39;t.", 
            "dur": "5.324", 
            "start": "159.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a satellite picture showing North Korea at night", 
            "dur": "4.344", 
            "start": "164.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "compared to neighbors.", 
            "dur": "3.412", 
            "start": "169.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the Amrok River,", 
            "dur": "1.943", 
            "start": "172.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which serves as a part of the border", 
            "dur": "2.371", 
            "start": "174.379"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "between North Korea and China.", 
            "dur": "2.684", 
            "start": "176.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you can see, the river can be very narrow", 
            "dur": "2.464", 
            "start": "179.434"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at certain points, allowing North Koreans to secretly cross.", 
            "dur": "5.996", 
            "start": "181.898"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But many die.", 
            "dur": "1.624", 
            "start": "187.894"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sometimes, I saw dead bodies floating down the river.", 
            "dur": "7.466", 
            "start": "189.518"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can&#39;t reveal many details [about] how I left North Korea,", 
            "dur": "4.94", 
            "start": "196.984"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I only can say that during the ugly years of the famine", 
            "dur": "4.263", 
            "start": "201.924"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was sent to China to live with distant relatives.", 
            "dur": "5.303", 
            "start": "206.187"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I only thought", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "211.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I would be separated from my family for a short time.", 
            "dur": "4.287", 
            "start": "213.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could have never imagined", 
            "dur": "1.692", 
            "start": "217.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that it would take 14 years to live together.", 
            "dur": "4.493", 
            "start": "219.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In China, it was hard living as a young girl without my family.", 
            "dur": "4.424", 
            "start": "223.662"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had no idea what life was going to be like", 
            "dur": "3.343", 
            "start": "228.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as a North Korean refugee,", 
            "dur": "1.837", 
            "start": "231.429"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I soon learned it&#39;s not only extremely difficult,", 
            "dur": "3.536", 
            "start": "233.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s also very dangerous,", 
            "dur": "2.647", 
            "start": "236.802"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "since North Korean refugees are considered in China", 
            "dur": "4.89", 
            "start": "239.449"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as illegal migrants.", 
            "dur": "2.839", 
            "start": "244.339"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I was living in constant fear", 
            "dur": "2.274", 
            "start": "247.178"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that my identity could be revealed,", 
            "dur": "2.543", 
            "start": "249.452"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I would be repatriated to a horrible fate", 
            "dur": "3.137", 
            "start": "251.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "back in North Korea.", 
            "dur": "2.756", 
            "start": "255.132"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One day, my worst nightmare came true,", 
            "dur": "2.712", 
            "start": "257.888"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when I was caught by the Chinese police", 
            "dur": "2.838", 
            "start": "260.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and brought to the police station for interrogation.", 
            "dur": "3.999", 
            "start": "263.438"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Someone had accused me of being North Korean,", 
            "dur": "3.438", 
            "start": "267.437"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so they tested my Chinese language abilities", 
            "dur": "3.685", 
            "start": "270.875"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and asked me tons of questions.", 
            "dur": "3.323", 
            "start": "274.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was so scared,", 
            "dur": "2.273", 
            "start": "277.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought my heart was going to explode.", 
            "dur": "3.008", 
            "start": "280.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If anything seemed unnatural, I could be imprisoned", 
            "dur": "3.498", 
            "start": "283.164"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and repatriated.", 
            "dur": "2.184", 
            "start": "286.662"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought my life was over,", 
            "dur": "2.447", 
            "start": "288.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I managed to control all the emotions inside me", 
            "dur": "3.239", 
            "start": "291.293"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and answer the questions.", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "294.532"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After they finished questioning me,", 
            "dur": "2.172", 
            "start": "296.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one official said to another,", 
            "dur": "2.125", 
            "start": "298.662"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;This was a false report.", 
            "dur": "2.078", 
            "start": "300.787"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She&#39;s not North Korean.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.932", 
            "start": "302.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they let me go. It was a miracle.", 
            "dur": "4.222", 
            "start": "304.797"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some North Koreans in China seek asylum", 
            "dur": "2.871", 
            "start": "309.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in foreign embassies,", 
            "dur": "2.323", 
            "start": "311.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but many can be caught by the Chinese police", 
            "dur": "3.316", 
            "start": "314.213"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and repatriated.", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "317.529"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These girls were so lucky.", 
            "dur": "2.177", 
            "start": "318.989"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even though they were caught,", 
            "dur": "1.616", 
            "start": "321.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they were eventually released", 
            "dur": "1.354", 
            "start": "322.782"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "after heavy international pressure.", 
            "dur": "3.348", 
            "start": "324.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These North Koreans were not so lucky.", 
            "dur": "3.341", 
            "start": "327.484"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Every year, countless North Koreans are caught in China", 
            "dur": "3.915", 
            "start": "330.825"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and repatriated to North Korea,", 
            "dur": "2.712", 
            "start": "334.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where they can be tortured, imprisoned", 
            "dur": "3.534", 
            "start": "337.452"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or publicly executed.", 
            "dur": "2.791", 
            "start": "340.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even though I was really fortunate to get out,", 
            "dur": "3.104", 
            "start": "343.777"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "many other North Koreans have not been so lucky.", 
            "dur": "3.058", 
            "start": "346.881"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s tragic that North Koreans have to hide their identities", 
            "dur": "3.801", 
            "start": "349.939"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and struggle so hard just to survive.", 
            "dur": "4.194", 
            "start": "353.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even after learning a new language and getting a job,", 
            "dur": "3.038", 
            "start": "357.934"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "their whole world can be turned upside down in an instant.", 
            "dur": "3.881", 
            "start": "360.972"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s why, after 10 years of hiding my identity,", 
            "dur": "3.736", 
            "start": "364.853"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I decided to risk going to South Korea,", 
            "dur": "4.282", 
            "start": "368.589"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I started a new life yet again.", 
            "dur": "3.075", 
            "start": "372.871"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Settling down in South Korea was a lot more challenging", 
            "dur": "3.143", 
            "start": "375.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than I had expected.", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "379.089"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "English was so important in South Korea,", 
            "dur": "3.429", 
            "start": "381.149"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I had to start learning my third language.", 
            "dur": "3.283", 
            "start": "384.578"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Also, I realized there was a wide gap", 
            "dur": "3.177", 
            "start": "387.861"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "between North and South.", 
            "dur": "1.983", 
            "start": "391.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We are all Korean, but inside,", 
            "dur": "2.177", 
            "start": "393.021"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we have become very different", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "395.198"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "due to 67 years of division.", 
            "dur": "3.592", 
            "start": "397.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I even went through an identity crisis.", 
            "dur": "4.039", 
            "start": "400.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Am I South Korean or North Korean?", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "404.669"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Where am I from? Who am I?", 
            "dur": "2.959", 
            "start": "407.909"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Suddenly, there was no country", 
            "dur": "2.036", 
            "start": "410.868"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could proudly call my own.", 
            "dur": "5.411", 
            "start": "412.904"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even though adjusting to life in South Korea was not easy,", 
            "dur": "3.991", 
            "start": "418.315"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I made a plan.", 
            "dur": "1.176", 
            "start": "422.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I started studying for the university entrance exam.", 
            "dur": "3.453", 
            "start": "423.482"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just as I was starting to get used to my new life,", 
            "dur": "4.015", 
            "start": "426.935"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I received a shocking phone call.", 
            "dur": "2.543", 
            "start": "430.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The North Korean authorities", 
            "dur": "1.421", 
            "start": "433.493"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "intercepted some money that I sent to my family,", 
            "dur": "2.712", 
            "start": "434.914"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and, as a punishment, my family was going", 
            "dur": "2.732", 
            "start": "437.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to be forcibly removed", 
            "dur": "2.337", 
            "start": "440.358"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to a desolate location in the countryside.", 
            "dur": "3.468", 
            "start": "442.695"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They had to get out quickly,", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "446.163"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I started planning how to help them escape.", 
            "dur": "3.565", 
            "start": "448.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "North Koreans have to travel incredible distances", 
            "dur": "3.482", 
            "start": "452.448"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on the path to freedom.", 
            "dur": "2.629", 
            "start": "455.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s almost impossible to cross the border", 
            "dur": "2.823", 
            "start": "458.559"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "between North Korea and South Korea,", 
            "dur": "2.858", 
            "start": "461.382"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so, ironically, I took a flight back to China", 
            "dur": "3.466", 
            "start": "464.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I headed toward the North Korean border.", 
            "dur": "3.622", 
            "start": "467.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Since my family couldn&#39;t speak Chinese,", 
            "dur": "2.864", 
            "start": "471.328"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had to guide them,", 
            "dur": "2.216", 
            "start": "474.192"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "somehow, through more than 2,000 miles in China", 
            "dur": "3.803", 
            "start": "476.408"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then into Southeast Asia.", 
            "dur": "3.263", 
            "start": "480.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The journey by bus took one week,", 
            "dur": "2.542", 
            "start": "483.474"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we were almost caught several times.", 
            "dur": "3.015", 
            "start": "486.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One time, our bus was stopped", 
            "dur": "2.641", 
            "start": "489.031"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and boarded by a Chinese police officer.", 
            "dur": "4.459", 
            "start": "491.672"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He took everyone&#39;s I.D. cards,", 
            "dur": "2.103", 
            "start": "496.131"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he started asking them questions.", 
            "dur": "2.633", 
            "start": "498.234"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Since my family couldn&#39;t understand Chinese,", 
            "dur": "3.595", 
            "start": "500.867"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought my family was going to be arrested.", 
            "dur": "4.134", 
            "start": "504.462"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As the Chinese officer approached my family,", 
            "dur": "2.981", 
            "start": "508.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I impulsively stood up, and I told him", 
            "dur": "2.509", 
            "start": "511.577"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that these are deaf and dumb people", 
            "dur": "2.667", 
            "start": "514.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I was chaperoning.", 
            "dur": "2.205", 
            "start": "516.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He looked at me suspiciously,", 
            "dur": "2.174", 
            "start": "518.958"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but luckily he believed me.", 
            "dur": "3.884", 
            "start": "521.132"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We made it all the way to the border of Laos,", 
            "dur": "3.111", 
            "start": "525.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I had to spend almost all my money", 
            "dur": "4.627", 
            "start": "528.127"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to bribe the border guards in Laos.", 
            "dur": "2.744", 
            "start": "532.754"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even after we got past the border,", 
            "dur": "2.853", 
            "start": "535.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my family was arrested and jailed", 
            "dur": "2.905", 
            "start": "538.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for illegal border crossing.", 
            "dur": "2.509", 
            "start": "541.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After I paid the fine and bribe,", 
            "dur": "2.216", 
            "start": "543.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my family was released in one month,", 
            "dur": "3.589", 
            "start": "545.981"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but soon after, my family was arrested and jailed again", 
            "dur": "3.816", 
            "start": "549.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the capital of Laos.", 
            "dur": "2.439", 
            "start": "553.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This was one of the lowest points in my life.", 
            "dur": "4.568", 
            "start": "555.825"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I did everything to get my family to freedom,", 
            "dur": "5.389", 
            "start": "560.393"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we came so close,", 
            "dur": "2.374", 
            "start": "565.782"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but my family was thrown in jail", 
            "dur": "2.297", 
            "start": "568.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just a short distance from the South Korean embassy.", 
            "dur": "3.544", 
            "start": "570.453"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I went back and forth between the immigration office", 
            "dur": "3.026", 
            "start": "573.997"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the police station,", 
            "dur": "1.731", 
            "start": "577.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "desperately trying to get my family out,", 
            "dur": "3.028", 
            "start": "578.754"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I didn&#39;t have enough money", 
            "dur": "1.452", 
            "start": "581.782"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to pay a bribe or fine anymore.", 
            "dur": "2.627", 
            "start": "583.234"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I lost all hope.", 
            "dur": "1.794", 
            "start": "585.861"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At that moment, I heard one man&#39;s voice ask me,", 
            "dur": "3.701", 
            "start": "587.655"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What&#39;s wrong?&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.491", 
            "start": "591.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was so surprised", 
            "dur": "1.597", 
            "start": "592.847"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that a total stranger cared enough to ask.", 
            "dur": "3.933", 
            "start": "594.444"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In my broken English, and with a dictionary,", 
            "dur": "2.554", 
            "start": "598.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I explained the situation, and without hesitating,", 
            "dur": "3.954", 
            "start": "600.931"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the man went to the ATM", 
            "dur": "2.053", 
            "start": "604.885"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he paid the rest of the money for my family", 
            "dur": "2.995", 
            "start": "606.938"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and two other North Koreans to get out of jail.", 
            "dur": "4.064", 
            "start": "609.933"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thanked him with all my heart, and I asked him,", 
            "dur": "3.404", 
            "start": "613.997"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Why are you helping me?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.374", 
            "start": "617.401"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I&#39;m not helping you,&quot; he said.", 
            "dur": "2.295", 
            "start": "619.775"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I&#39;m helping the North Korean people.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.251", 
            "start": "622.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I realized that this was a symbolic moment in my life.", 
            "dur": "4.498", 
            "start": "625.321"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The kind stranger symbolized new hope for me", 
            "dur": "3.589", 
            "start": "629.819"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the North Korean people when we needed it most,", 
            "dur": "3.398", 
            "start": "633.408"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he showed me the kindness of strangers", 
            "dur": "3.251", 
            "start": "636.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the support of the international community", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "640.057"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are truly the rays of hope we North Korean people need.", 
            "dur": "5.221", 
            "start": "642.667"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Eventually, after our long journey,", 
            "dur": "2.486", 
            "start": "647.888"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my family and I were reunited in South Korea,", 
            "dur": "3.397", 
            "start": "650.374"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but getting to freedom is only half the battle.", 
            "dur": "3.454", 
            "start": "653.771"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Many North Koreans are separated from their families,", 
            "dur": "3.623", 
            "start": "657.225"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and when they arrive in a new country,", 
            "dur": "2.813", 
            "start": "660.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they start with little or no money.", 
            "dur": "3.644", 
            "start": "663.661"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we can benefit from the international community", 
            "dur": "3.026", 
            "start": "667.305"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for education, English language training,", 
            "dur": "3.005", 
            "start": "670.331"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "job training, and more.", 
            "dur": "2.363", 
            "start": "673.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We can also act as a bridge", 
            "dur": "2.114", 
            "start": "675.699"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "between the people inside North Korea", 
            "dur": "2.125", 
            "start": "677.813"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the outside world,", 
            "dur": "1.98", 
            "start": "679.938"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because many of us stay in contact", 
            "dur": "2.724", 
            "start": "681.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with family members still inside,", 
            "dur": "2.769", 
            "start": "684.642"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we send information and money", 
            "dur": "2.182", 
            "start": "687.411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that is helping to change North Korea from inside.", 
            "dur": "4.568", 
            "start": "689.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve been so lucky, received so much help", 
            "dur": "3.037", 
            "start": "694.161"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and inspiration in my life,", 
            "dur": "2.205", 
            "start": "697.198"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I want to help give aspiring North Koreans", 
            "dur": "3.344", 
            "start": "699.403"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a chance to prosper", 
            "dur": "2.776", 
            "start": "702.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with international support.", 
            "dur": "3.038", 
            "start": "705.523"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m confident that you will see more and more", 
            "dur": "2.486", 
            "start": "708.561"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "North Koreans succeeding all over the world,", 
            "dur": "2.757", 
            "start": "711.047"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "including the TED stage.", 
            "dur": "2.351", 
            "start": "713.804"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you.", 
            "dur": "2.622", 
            "start": "716.155"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "9.722", 
            "start": "718.777"
        }
    ], 
